<h3>Setup</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Use most valuable bonus marker for each region</li>
    <li>Deck I atop deck II ...</li>
    <li>Remove deck [N+1] and above</li>
    <li>(Salsa) Deal 2 Blue forum tiles to each player, keep one</li>
</ul>

<div class="table table-100" id="setuptable">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-1"><h4>Base</h4></div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Cards with column</li>
                <li>Replace 4 Venus cards with no-symbol cards</li>
                <li>Mason shuffled into stack I, not stack II</li>
                <li>Remove Magister cards</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-2">
            <ul>
                <li>Architect</li>
                <li>Diplomat</li>
                <li>Mercator</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-2">
            <ul>
                <li>Prefect</li>
                <li>Prefect</li>
                <li>Senator</li>
                <li>Tribute</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-1"><h4>Venus solo</h4></div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Cards with column</li>
                <li>8 starting cards (with column)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-2">
            <ul>
                <li>Architect</li>
                <li>Diplomat</li>
                <li>Mercator</li>
                <li>Magister</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-2">
            <ul>
                <li>Prefect</li>
                <li>Prefect</li>
                <li>Senator</li>
                <li>Tribute</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-1"><h4>Venus team</h4></div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Cards with rings</li>
                <li>2nd partner chooses a city not-adjacent to start city for both colonists</li>
                <li>If it is land-only or sea-only, they can use 2 people or 2 boats</li>
                <li>6 starting cards (with rings)</li>
                <li>Partner 1: remove Diplomat</li>
                <li>Partner 2: remove Architect</li>
                <li>Both partners start with same amount of money: $5 / 6 / 7</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-2">
            <ul>
                <li><u>Partner 1</u></li>
                <li>Architect</li>
                <li>Mercator</li>
                <li>Prefect</li>
                <li>Praetor</li>
                <li>Tribune</li>
                <li>Legatus</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-2">
            <ul>
                <li><u>Partner 2</u></li>
                <li>Diplomat</li>
                <li>Mercator</li>
                <li>Prefect</li>
                <li>Praetor</li>
                <li>Tribune</li>
                <li>Legatus</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

