<h3>Cards</h3>
<div class="table table-100">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Tribune
                    <ul>
                        <li>Receive money</li>
                        <li>Colonist on start city</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Architect
                    <ul>
                        <li>X movement points, X = # of colonists on board</li>
                        <li>May move through occupied lines (for 1 movement point)</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Prefect
                    <ul>
                        <li>All buildings in province produce</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Colonist
                    <ul>
                        <li>New colonists on start city or with player's houses</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Diplomat
                    <ul>
                        <li>Cannot copy Diplomat</li>
                        <li>(Venus) Player chooses the card to copy, both execute it</li>
                        <li>(Venus) Card cannot be copied again by partner on their turn</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Senator
                    <ul>
                        <li>Slide & fill after at turn end</li>
                        <li>Cards go to hand</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Mercator
                    <ul>
                        <li>Receive money</li>
                        <li>Choose two good <u>types</u></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Consul
                    <ul>
                        <li>Pay only goods printed on card</li>
                        <li>Card goes to hand</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Magister (Venus solo)
                    <ul>
                        <li>Repeat your own previous non-Senator card</li>
                        <li>May Magister a Diplomat to copy a Senator</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Praetor (team)
                    <ul>
                        <li>Cards are refilled after both partners are finished</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Proconsul (team)
                    <ul>
                        <li>Cannot purchase a proconsul</li>
                        <li>Partner plays a card (not Legatus) and resolves it solo</li>
                        <li>Play order does not change</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Legatus (team)
                    <ul>
                        <li>Inspect partner's hand and make suggestion</li>
                        <li>Partner chooses & plays a card, then team executes card</li>
                        <li>(A) plays Legatus, (B) plays architect:
                            <ol>
                                <li>(B) resolves architect</li>
                                <li>(A) resolves architect</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li>Play order does not change, follow orange pawn</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Double Choice (Venus)
                    <ul>
                        <li>Solo: Pick either</li>
                        <li>Team: Partner cannot make the same choice</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

